Company Overview of ESL Investments, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ESL Investments Inc. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets. It also invests in convertible securities, derivatives, swaps, and options. The firm invests in value stocks by employing fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach. The firm obtains external research to complement its in-house research to make its investments. ESL Investments, Inc. was founded in April 1988 and is based in Bay Harbour, Florida.


1170 Kane ConcourseSuite 200Bay Harbor Islands, FL 33154United StatesFounded in 1988



