ESL Investments, Inc. Key Developments

ESL Partners & Fairholme Capital Reportedly Considering Deal With Sears Canada
Jul 10 17
ESL Partners L.P., a fund sponsored by ESL Investments, Inc., and Fairholme Capital Management, L.L.C. said on July 10, 2017 that they are talking with the legal team at troubled retailer Sears Canada Inc. about potential options, according to BNN TV. BNN said the deal could involve, for example, asset purchases.


